{"tid":2198593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禁令將生效！三星顯示器傳向美申請許可 以便向華為出貨","createTime":"2020-09-11T12:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:24:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09721f370ce3bfc4a78eeda9d7359624e63e58c7","tid":2198593,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"隨著美國的華為禁令即將生效，據傳三星電子旗下的三星顯示器（Samsung Display），已向美國申請出口許可證，以便向華為繼續供應產品。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，南韓週四有業界消息指出，三星顯示器正尋求豁免向華為出貨，但三星顯示器拒絕對此置評。據報導，三星電子及蘋果皆是三星顯示器OLED顯示屏的主要客戶。<br />\n<br />\n三星顯示器的競爭對手「LG顯示器」週三則在1份聲明表示，由於他們對華為的面板出貨量有限，因此美國禁令對其造成的影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n美國在8月份進一步擴大對華為的限制，禁止供應商未經許可向華為出售使用美國技術製造的晶片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3288519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3288519&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=31abdfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3288519&h=60f9ecbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3288519</a>"},{"pid":"3a37e66b121390353c6b6fd47f6b56df2f798bea","tid":2198593,"uid":54517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"出你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aace8033ffd937d51d303f0fbcd8a9ee14d1a287","tid":2198593,"uid":51937,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"韓國真係垃圾"},{"pid":"acaa0d8819243424d7ed811677b000991d3ac5c1","tid":2198593,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾羞星"},{"pid":"54b2e56dd989756c13528421364761e0f2edcee9","tid":2198593,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"罷買三星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587456f7c5ff1f05bd05d4451648bdf1b72f0cc4","tid":2198593